.SH NAME
openssl\-ecparam \- EC parameter manipulation and generation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
\&\fBopenssl ecparam\fR
[\fB\-help\fR]
[\fB\-inform\fR \fBDER\fR|\fBPEM\fR]
